title: Pumpkin Squares
ingredients: ['125g (4¼ oz) butter, softened', '100g (3¾ oz) dark brown soft sugar', '125g (4¼ oz) plain flour', '50g (2 oz) porridge oats', '2 eggs', '150g (5 oz) caster sugar', '1 (400g) tin pumpkin purée', '350ml (12 fl oz) evaporated milk', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '1/4 teaspoon ground cloves']
